<s> Hi, setAttributeNS() and friends with similar parameters has text to stricly forbid a qName with a prefix for a null nsURI, but nothing on whether it  </s>
<s> is legal to use it with a defined nsURI, and a qName that doesn't contain a prefix part.  </s>
<s> Most implementations seem to accept it, and then fail to serialise it properly.  </s>
